"Object-orientiertes Studenten Betriebsystem"

This is the new release of the OOStuBs fo the EOS of the Otto-von-Guericke-University Magdeburg. It is used as part of the practical exercises of the lecture "Betriebsysteme I".

Further information concerning the implementation and the used specifications for the hardware drivers are available at: http://www-ivs.cs.uni-magdeburg.de/eos/lehre/WS1011/vl_bs/uebung/
